            </div>

            <div id="collapse1" class="collapse">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <form action="/subscript" method="post" id="payment-form">
                        <br>
                        <h3>Place-A-Penny</h3>
                        <h4>Remembering the Children of the Holocaust</h4>
                        <h5>Place-a-Penny on the Star of David Memorial walls remembering one child who perished in the Holocaust - $18. The word "chai" means life and has a number value of 18, which is very important in Hebrew culture.</h5>
                        <br>
                        <input type="text" name="option" value="penny" hidden>
                        <input type="text" name="quantity" id="quantity" value="0" hidden>
                        <h4>Choose a Sponsorship Level</h4>
